1
00:00:06,840 --> 00:00:07,640
Technology

2
00:00:07,840 --> 00:00:09,160
has greatly improved the standard of living for humanity

3
00:00:09,160 --> 00:00:10,440
by a significant margin.

4
00:00:12,480 --> 00:00:14,280
But at the same time, it has made people give up their sense of self.

5
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:16,480
Letting technology dominate and control

6
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:17,800
our free and joyful souls.

7
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:25,760
What do you think?

8
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,160
Are there any flaws?

9
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:31,000
You'll know if you try.

10
00:00:33,680 --> 00:00:36,840
Nianqiu, why did you come so early today?

11
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,880
You... you all are

12
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:45,960
Xingye's friends?

13
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:47,840
Ah, yes.

14
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:50,440
He went out.

15
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:52,320
Do you need something from him?

16
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:53,200
I...

17
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,360
I have a gift I want to give him.

18
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,160
Then give it to me.

19
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:58,840
I'll pass it on to him for you.

20
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:01,200
Don't worry.

21
00:01:03,755 --> 00:01:04,840
Thank you.

22
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:28,240
You see,

23
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:31,400
life is full of misfortunes,

24
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:37,680
but people still strive for happiness.

25
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,240
As for things like happiness index,

26
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,040
to me,

27
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,680
it's just a cold number.

28
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,520
I think

29
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:50,960
as long as you live well,

30
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:54,000
those numbers can always be changed.

31
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,480
If

32
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,760
there could be a world without pain

33
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,920
and worries, a perfect world,

34
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,040
wouldn't that be even better?

35
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:21,440
A place where you feel at ease is a perfect world, isn't it?

36
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,160
Alright, I've been up all night.

37
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,480
My old back can't take it anymore.

38
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,080
I need to go back and get a good sleep.

39
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,760
Although this thing of yours is fixed,

40
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,640
its version is too outdated.

41
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,760
It won't last long.

42
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,200
And don't miss your pumpkin carriage.

43
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,320
Attorney Jin, you're here.

44
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,360
There's still some time before the auction starts.

45
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,440
We still have a while to go.

46
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,400
You can rest at the bar for a bit if you like.

47
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,600
I'll just wait here.

48
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,400
Please follow me.

49
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:08,240
Please have a seat here.

50
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,440
These are the items up for auction tonight.

51
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,640
You can take a look first.

52
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,320
If there's anything you don't understand,

53
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:18,600
or if you have any requests,

54
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,080
feel free to come to me anytime.

55
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,080
Anything at all.

56
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:45,920
Flesh trade.

57
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,760
But these records are way too detailed.

58
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,360
Wait a moment, miss.

59
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,560
Sorry, miss.

60
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,040
No invitation.

61
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,760
You can't go in.

62
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:55,960
Sorry, miss.

63
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,600
You're not on the guest list.

64
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,640
Please cooperate with us for identity verification.

65
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,040
I've said it many times already.

66
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:11,520
I've already been verified.

67
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,160
What's going on?

68
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,080
Did you wash your hands?

69
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,080
What did you say?

70
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:26,040
You dare touch my girlfriend with such dirty hands?

71
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,240
Is this how your boss Bai usually

72
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,440
