73
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,240
Jin,

74
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,280
why are you so angry?

75
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,600
Boss.

76
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,280
Is she someone new you found?

77
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,040
Attorney Jin.

78
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,400
Don't you know him?

79
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,160
Boss.

80
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,760
New girlfriend

81
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:14,720
Yeah

82
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,000
Don't touch me

83
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,520
Where did you go just now?

84
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,480
Baby

85
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,040
Don't be mad

86
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,520
So just now, Lao Bai

87
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,200
