88
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:25,880
Right?

89
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:26,960
Yeah

90
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:28,840
Don't make things hard for your subordinates

91
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,280
Later

92
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,640
I'll teach them a lesson

93
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,280
But Lao Jin

94
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,640
this private photo session

95
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,000
