96
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,600
You know

97
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,640
I hate people who break the rules the most

98
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,160
Yeah

99
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,680
Have them verify their identity

100
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,560
If they don't cooperate

101
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,200
Do you know who she is?

102
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,600
She's the key person in your dispute

103
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,440
with Sanxin Group

104
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,640
Treat her well

105
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,880
