106
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,000
Lao Jin

107
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:27,680
This is the Boss Bai you always mention

108
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,280
Yeah

109
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:31,720
This is my best brother

110
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:32,840
Boss Bai

111
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,480
Now this

112
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,560
is what someone

113
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:58,880
