114
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:03,960
He knelt down to you

115
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:05,640
Are you satisfied now?

116
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,720
Or

117
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,960
get rid of him

118
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,040
You do it

119
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,960
It's not that serious.

120
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:27,680
It's not a big deal, Lao Bai.

121
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,880
It's not that serious.

122
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:31,520
Lao Jin is so easygoing today.

123
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,760
